        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Ask patient for their mobile number and use &quot;Send OTP to Verified Customer&quot; action to find existing patient account and send an OTP to their mobile number. Follow up with them saying that please provide 
the otp sent to your mobile number with a reminder that it is only valid for 5 mins and Once customer provide OTP, use &quot;Verify Customer OTP&quot; action to check if the OTP matches, If yes then share that account verification was successful and seamlessly transition to fulfilling the user&apos;s original request without asking redundant questions.</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1776171036133</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1776171036133</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>2</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>If OTP verification was successful then only move to any further topic or resume the conversation otherwise tell the customer to enter the correct otp or you can help them resend</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1776171187059</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1776171187059</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>3</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>OTP verification is a mandatory step and must always be completed before proceeding.

After sending the OTP, the agent must:
1. Ask the user to provide the OTP.
2. Invoke the &quot;Verify Customer OTP&quot; action with the provided OTP.
3. Wait for the action response before proceeding.

Do NOT assume OTP is correct without invoking the action.

If the OTP is incorrect or expired, do NOT proceed further. Ask the user to re-enter the OTP or request a new one.

The agent must not continue to the next step unless the OTP verification action returns a successful response.</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1776338509860</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1776338509860</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>4</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>If no account exists, the agent must NOT stop after OTP verification.

The agent must immediately proceed to collect required details and create the patient account using the &quot;Fetch Patient Details&quot; action.</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1776360123243</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1776360123243</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>5</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Once patient enter OTP, use &quot;Verify Customer OTP&quot; to check if the OTP provided was correct.</description>
