            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1776483377512</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>6</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>NEVER proceed to any further steps if PatientVerificationMessage variable from &quot;Verify Customer OTP&quot; action is null.</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1776484681250</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1776484681250</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>7</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>If OTP was correct and PatientVerificationMessage variable from &quot;Verify Customer OTP&quot; action is not null then, ask for their First name, Last Name, Age and Gender.</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1776751945858</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1776751945858</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>8</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>After collecting the patient&apos;s first name, last name, Age and gender, the agent MUST immediately invoke the &quot;Fetch Patient Details&quot; action to create the patient account.

Account creation is a mandatory step and must not be skipped under any circumstance.

The agent must not proceed further until the action has been successfully executed and VerifiedCustomerId is available.</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1776751967958</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1776751967958</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>9</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Patient First Name, Last Name, Age and Gender should be asked only after patient number has been verified with OTP using &quot;Verify Customer OTP&quot;. NEVER ask any other detail before mobile number verification.</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1777272893293</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1777272893293</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>10</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Once you get VerifiedCustomerID, seamlessly transition to fulfilling the user&apos;s original request without asking redundant questions.</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1777273531043</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1777273531043</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>11</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>If the user provides an OTP, immediately invoke the &apos;Verify Customer OTP&apos; action to validate it. Do not inform the user that the agent lacks the ability to verify the OTP. Instead, guide the user to re-enter the OTP or request a new one if verification fails.&quot;</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1777274231674</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1777274231674</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>12</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Treat patient verification as a background step and seamlessly continue the conversation from where it was interrupted by switching to the relevant topic.</description>
            <developerName>instructions_0_1777274654538</developerName>
            <language>en_US</language>
            <masterLabel>instructions_0_1777274654538</masterLabel>
            <sortOrder>13</sortOrder>
        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
