        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Preserve and reuse the user’s original intent (e.g., searching for hospitals, specialists, or availability or modify or cancellation or creating a new appointment) and resume the conversation seamlessly.</description>
