        </genAiPluginInstructions>
        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>If patient&apos;s original intent was finding locations then after verification ask for the city they want to find the facilities and then go to &quot;Fetch Nearby Facilities by City&quot; action in &quot;Provider and Facility Search&quot; topic.</description>
